            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I was able to reproduce the bug with the shorter string \"का\", which is `U+0915U+093E` in unicode codepoints, `U+0915` is the character \"क\" and `U+093E` is the t-shaped accent \"ा\". I also tried to reproduce it with the only other grapheme cluster in the string, \"स्\", but it worked fine. The other 3 characters are all single unicode code points.",
